    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the company, the funding, all of it. i just saw the final notice from the creditors and i feel like i can't even breathe. i was supposed to be the one who made it, you know? instead i just blew everything and ruined everything for my family. i don't even know how to face them. how do you even walk back into your own house after failing this hard?",
